*ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r3 (18 Feb 2003)

  18 Feb 2003; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r3.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r3 :
  new ebuild for IBM jdk to include ppc support, set only as ppc now.. no sense in making x86 reinstall for nothing

  12 Dec 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> :
  Updated Slots on all ebuilds. Fixes #11984.

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
  03 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :
  Removed invalid sourcing of the eclasses (this is depricated).

*ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r2 (23 Dec 2002)

  23 Dec 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r2.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r2:
  Switched to the new nsplugins layout.

*ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r1 (02 Dec 2002)

  23 Dec 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r1.ebuild
  Unmasking from package.mask, going to testing phase.
  Install java plugin as it doesnt segfault like 1.3.x plugin. Installing as
  the old fashion way, not the new way made by phoenix.

  03 Dec 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r1.ebuild
  Fixed a typo in the ebuild and in ChangeLog. Thanks azarah !!.

  02 Dec 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> 
  Added: ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r1.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.4.0-r1
  Modified: files/ibm-jdk-1.4.0
  Fixed an error on setting classpath. IBM cuts the (rt.jar on sun-jdk) on
  various files that need to be added to classpath.

*ibm-jdk-1.4.0 (24 Nov 2002)

  24 Nov 2002; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.4.0.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.4.0 files/ibm-jdk-1.4.0:
  New upstream version of ibm-jdk. Closes #11149, Marking it as testing.
  Thanks to Steven Wong <wongs15@tartarus.uwa.edu.au> for the ebuild.

*ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r2 (21 Nov 2002)

  21 Nov 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r2.ebuild,
  files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r2 :
  Switched to the new nsplugins layout.

*ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1 (12 May 2002)

  07 Sep 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild :
  Updated java-config dependency to fix inadvertent CLASSPATH bugs.

  06 Sep 2002; Owen Stampflee <owen@gentoo.org> files/ibm-jdk-1.3.0 files/ibm-jdk-1.3.1 :
  Added "." to the CLASSPATH in the env.d scripts.

  01 Sep 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed typo that prevented java-config from recognizing the installed
  VM. Fixes #7241.
 
  26 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added doc keyword to optionally install documentation. Set slot to 1.3, so
  it can coexist with other IBM JDKs (if they come). Fixes #6668. Now
  provides virtual/jre-1.3.1, virtual/jdk-1.3.1.

  01 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added LICENSE, KEYWORDS and SLOT.

  14 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1:
  Fixed the creation of a spurious /usr/ibm-jdk-1.3.1/share.

  12 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild, files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1:
  Disabled browser plugin as it does not work.
  Removed ibm-jdk-1.3.1.ebuild, files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1

